urls.title: Chai Lifeline : Fighting Illness With Love

data.text: @Chai_Lifeline @Chai_Lifeline is an international children’s health support network, providing emotional, social, and financial assistance to more than 5,800 children with life-threatening or lifelong illnesses. To learn more about Chai Lifeline and its services, visit https://t.co/4EVQLRGRD6

@Chai_Lifeline The trip is Chai Lifeline’s celebration of life for those who have completed cancer treatment, with each participant invited to share the memorable journey with a parent. Upon arrival in Israel, the group will hit the ground running, getting the full Israel experience in 10 days.

Today, EL AL had the pleasure of partnering with @Chai_Lifeline to fly a group of twelve inspiring teenagers to Israel as part of the annual Hartman Family Foundation Wish at the Wall program. https://t.co/al2OvHCg7v
